  • Benchmarks: Bluff, OLS and ARIMA(1,1,1)

In [257]:
# Calculate MAPE for HR and HDG
def calculate_mape_HR(my_df, target):
    temp_sum = np.sum(np.absolute((my_df.iloc[-6:].dropna()[target] - my_df.iloc[-6:].dropna()["HR"])
                                  /my_df.iloc[-6:].dropna()["HR"]))
    my_mape = 100 / len(my_df.iloc[-6:].dropna()) * temp_sum
    return my_mape

def calculate_mape_HDG(my_df, target):
    temp_sum = np.sum(np.absolute((my_df.iloc[-6:].dropna()[target] - my_df.iloc[-6:].dropna()["HDG"])
                                  /my_df.iloc[-6:].dropna()["HDG"]))
    my_mape = 100 / len(my_df.iloc[-6:].dropna()) * temp_sum
    return my_mape

ARIMA(1,1,1)¶

  • Based on ADF test, both HR and HDG are autoregressive with 1 month lag, their 1st lag correlations are positive meaning steel markets are momentum driving rather than mean reverting
  • ARIMA(1,1,1) would be chosen
In [264]:
from statsmodels.tsa.arima_model import ARMA
In [265]:
ARIMA_HR = {}
ARIMA_HR_CI = {}
ARIMA_HDG = {}
ARIMA_HDG_CI = {}
hr_temp = {}
hr_temp_l = {}
hr_temp_h = {}
HR_Pred = {}
HR_Pred_L = {}
HR_Pred_H = {}
hdg_temp = {}
hdg_temp_l = {}
hdg_temp_h = {}
HDG_Pred = {}
HDG_Pred_L = {}
HDG_Pred_H = {}
forecast_start_date = {}
daterange ={}
In [267]:
for name in df_names:
    mod_arima_hr = ARMA(df_dict_pct[name]["HR"].dropna(), order=(1,1))
    res_arima_hr = mod_arima_hr.fit()
    ARIMA_HR[name] = res_arima_hr.forecast(6)[0]
    ARIMA_HR_CI[name] = res_arima_hr.forecast(6)[-1]
    hr_temp[name] = df_dict[name].dropna().iloc[0].HR
    hr_temp_l[name] = df_dict[name].dropna().iloc[0].HRa
    hr_temp_h[name] = df_dict[name].dropna().iloc[0].HR
    HR_Pred[name] = [hr_temp[name]]
    HR_Pred_L[name] = [hr_temp[name]]
    HR_Pred_H[name] = [hr_temp[name]]
    forecast_start_date[name] = df_dict[name].dropna().index[0]
    daterange[name] = pd.date_range(start = forecast_start_date[name],periods=7 , freq='MS')
    for pred_hr, ci in zip(ARIMA_HR[name], ARIMA_HR_CI[name]):
        hr_temp[name] = hr_temp[name] * (1+pred_hr)
        hr_temp_l[name] = hr_temp_l[name] * (1+ci[0])
        hr_temp_h[name] = hr_temp_h[name] * (1+ci[-1])
        HR_Pred[name].append(hr_temp[name])
        HR_Pred_L[name].append(hr_temp_l[name])
        HR_Pred_H[name].append(hr_temp_h[name])
    HR_Pred[name] = pd.DataFrame(HR_Pred[name], index = daterange[name], columns=["TSAHR"])
    HR_Pred_L[name] = pd.DataFrame(HR_Pred_L[name], index = daterange[name], columns=["TSAHR-L"])
    HR_Pred_H[name] = pd.DataFrame(HR_Pred_H[name], index = daterange[name], columns=["TSAHR-H"])
    
    # Instantiate model
    mod_arima_hdg = ARMA(df_dict_pct[name]["HDG"].dropna(), order=(1,1))
    # Fit model
    res_arima_hdg = mod_arima_hdg.fit()
    
    ARIMA_HDG[name] = res_arima_hdg.forecast(6)[0]
    ARIMA_HDG_CI[name] = res_arima_hdg.forecast(6)[-1]
    hdg_temp[name] = df_dict[name].dropna().iloc[0].HDG
    hdg_temp_l[name] = df_dict[name].dropna().iloc[0].HDG
    hdg_temp_h[name] = df_dict[name].dropna().iloc[0].HDG
    
    HDG_Pred[name] = [hdg_temp[name]]
    HDG_Pred_L[name] = [hdg_temp[name]]
    HDG_Pred_H[name] = [hdg_temp[name]]
    
    for pred_hdg, ci in zip(ARIMA_HDG[name], ARIMA_HDG_CI[name]):
        hdg_temp[name] = hdg_temp[name] * (1+pred_hdg)
        #hdg_temp[name] = df_dict[name].dropna().iloc[0].HDG * (1+pred_hdg)
        hdg_temp_l[name] = hdg_temp_l[name] * (1+ci[0])
        hdg_temp_h[name] = hdg_temp_h[name] * (1+ci[-1])
        HDG_Pred[name].append(hdg_temp[name])
        HDG_Pred_L[name].append(hdg_temp_l[name])
        HDG_Pred_H[name].append(hdg_temp_h[name])
        
    HDG_Pred[name] = pd.DataFrame(HDG_Pred[name], index = daterange[name], columns=["TSAHDG"])
    HDG_Pred_L[name] = pd.DataFrame(HDG_Pred_L[name], index = daterange[name], columns=["TSAHDG-L"])
    HDG_Pred_H[name] = pd.DataFrame(HDG_Pred_H[name], index = daterange[name], columns=["TSAHDG-H"])
    
    df_dict[name] = df_dict[name].\
    join(HR_Pred[name], how="outer").\
    join(HR_Pred_L[name], how="outer").\
    join(HR_Pred_H[name], how="outer").\
    join(HDG_Pred[name], how="outer").\
    join(HDG_Pred_L[name], how="outer").\
    join(HDG_Pred_H[name], how="outer")
